<item>
            <title>[FLINK-3439] Remove final Long.MAX_VALUE Watermark in StreamSource</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3439</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I think this was an oversight. At one point we decided to not emit in-flight windows when closing the topology or sources.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12940119">FLINK-3439</key>
            <summary>Remove final Long.MAX_VALUE Watermark in StreamSource</summary>
